wikipedia_page.main: Julia Margaret Cross  is a 6th degree black belt in ITF Taekwon-Do and a martial arts instructor. She is a six-time ITF Taekwon-Do World Champion and 15 time European Champion. Julia Cross is the only person, male or female, ever to achieve six world titles in ITF Taekwon-Do.

response: * Julia Cross, former ITF Taekwon-Do World Champion
